The paper deals with the problem of secure transmission over a wiretap channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of channel state information (CSI) and the analysis of the secure degrees of freedom (SDoF) suggest that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
